properties.pdsode:Description: "Single WAC observation from a multi-temporal image sequence to support illumination studies of the polar regions (see [SPEYERERETAL2013]). Each frame of the sequence is in polar stereographic projection and covers 80 to 90 degrees latitude. This WAC polar movie frame covers a strip of the north polar region at 2009-09-24 02:24 UTC."
